{"tid":2055052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國版Tumblr「lofter」慘遭舉報下架，各大中國網民鶴怨猿啼！","createTime":"2020-06-07T15:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T17:18:55.000Z","uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e09c94d5ccdcdfc4cbbdd013b90f94e9023ddc","tid":2055052,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"當年Tumblr紅透半天，於是網易係2011年開發咗「LOFTER」，中文又名為「樂乎」，係一款輕博客服務平台，6月5日有中國網民開始發現LOFTER APPS係部份國內應用市場遭到下架，但係無任何官方新聞解釋，惹嚟種種懷疑，雖然不少網民表示不用擔心，因為APPLE Store仍可以下載，而然6月7日包括APPLE Store 國內全線應用市場均下架LOFTER，網民心灰意冷確信是遭到強大力量(中共政府)下架，就有如年初發生的AO3事件。<br />\n<br />\n但因為目前仍然未有官方企出嚟解釋事件，所以眾多網民議論紛紛，有人推測係騰訊背後出手搞鳩其他公司，但最多人認為又係肖戰fans舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ud2npRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fud2npRf.png&h=ce7c81d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiukVXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiukVXW.png&h=42bba84a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然網頁板和本身已下載的LOFTER程式仍然可以繼續使用，但如果不能在應用市場上架，代表用戶將來不能維修更新軟件和流失新用戶加入，代表LOFTER的發展前路茫茫..."},{"pid":"f4498b5de53b28c410ce9df321213863ebcbd511","tid":2055052,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CouEr70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCouEr70.jpg&h=67328113&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565b9a6e95782d833518b2a4c451d31c4886e266","tid":2055052,"uid":77905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"中國版Tumblr即係點<br />\n有J圖？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3a68324eee937ef6b169b9573d1dd6234831e8","tid":2055052,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"565b9a6e95782d833518b2a4c451d31c4886e266","tid":2055052,"uid":77905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"中國版Tumblr即係點<br />\n有J圖